Problem
-------

Description of the problem. 

Given: A formalised input with $x$ as input. 

Return: A formlised output with $y$ as output. 

Sample Dataset
--------------

```
AGCTTTTCATTCTGACTGCAACGGGCAATATGTCTCTGTGTGGATTAAAAAAAGAGTGTCTGATAGCAGC

```

Sample Output
-------------

```
20 12 17 21

```
